      "data": {
        "tag": "Difference",
        "title": "What Makes It Different",
        "body": "Twilite overlaps with several categories without collapsing into any one of them. It is not merely a whiteboard, note app, workflow graph, documentation tool, mind map, or chat interface. It treats the graph itself as the durable semantic artifact: addressable, explorable, AI-readable, AI-editable, publishable, portable, and structurally meaningful.",
        "_classBinding": {
