        "tag": "Collaboration",
        "title": "Human + AI",
        "body": "Twilite is designed for humans and AI to work against the same persistent structure. Instead of generating isolated text blobs, AI can navigate graph structure, inspect relationships, update nodes, create connections, preserve references, and operate through explicit mutation contracts. That makes AI collaboration more durable, inspectable, reversible, and graph-native.",
        "_classBinding": {
