        "tag": "Depth",
        "title": "One Graph, Many Depths",
        "body": "Twilite supports layered understanding. At a glance you can hold product identity, major concepts, and high-level structure. Closer in, the same graph can reveal implementation details, supporting evidence, semantic relationships, and runtime behavior. That lets one graph support onboarding, exploration, authoring, and advanced architecture work.",
