      "data": {
        "tag": "Persistence",
        "title": "Why Persistence Matters",
        "body": "Most AI interaction today is disposable. Chats disappear. Context collapses. Ideas fragment. Meaning drifts. Twilite treats knowledge as something that should accumulate structurally over time. Humans and AI can continue evolving the same graph, the same relationships, and the same semantic terrain. The result is durable memory instead of temporary conversation.",
